Background

👋Hi I’m Vince, a data scientist. Currently, I’m analyzing NATO1 OOI2 object detectors using commercial satellite imagery on my AI Edge Kit team & human biometric performance data for JSOC3. Previously, I worked on a GEOINT4 performance modeling team for 5 years, where I wrote code to analyze large amounts of transactional data on geospatial imagery (billions of records) for the NGA5 to help improve the NSG6. On my team, I promoted open source software development best practices and data science tooling usage in Python & R. I managed my team’s government network GitLab & corporate GitHub organizations, which grew from 0 to 300+ repositories over my tenure. When I’m not traveling or salsa dancing, I’m working remotely. 🕺🧑‍💻
